Let's talk as we walk

74
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,200
Yu Tong

75
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,280
Wait for me

76
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,040
I'm coming

77
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,400
