82
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:32,240
Yu Tong

83
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,440
You might not feel your inner feelings right now

84
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,160
But if you really try to feel it again

85
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:36,920
You might feel differently

86
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,160
Stop following me

87
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,360
You already know who I am

88
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,760
What's the point of this?

89
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,400
You still have to rely on me

90
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,440
Stop

91
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,080
I've said before

92
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,840
Our ancestors lived here

93
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,320
