96
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,920
Why must you go out?

97
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,360
Why must you fight?

98
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,520
I want to stay here too

99
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:17,480
But I must fight for my homeland

100
