109
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,640
Take them back

110
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,160
Plant them in your yard

111
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,000
Think of it as me being with you

112
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,160
My roots are here

113
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:08,960
So I won't leave

114
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,120
Miss Yu Tong

115
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,240
Blades have no eyes

116
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,200
I

117
