118
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,120
I've long wanted to see

119
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,600
General Wei's strength

120
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,800
Come on

121
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,720
Just subdue her

122
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,080
No need to kill her

123
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:52,760
With my martial arts

124
