130
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:26,000
Why is it just you two these days?

131
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,280
He Qi seems to have left

132
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:27,800
Princess

133
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,840
Left?

134
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,400
Let him be

135
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,160
Do you two like it here?

136
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,760
We like it, Princess

137
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,160
Outside, we're on tenterhooks

138
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,080
Yeah

139
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,280
Here we don't have to fight

140
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,600
Even you want to spar with me?

141
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,160
Acting tough with me? Acting tough with me?

142
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,080
Acting tough with me?

143
