146
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,320
Tell me, what should I do?

147
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:19,120
You are still young.

148
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,200
How can you stay cooped up in this place?

149
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:24,360
