151
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,440
I should listen to the opposite of your words.

152
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,440
You are the worst.

153
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,120
Wait.

154
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,760
