173
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,640
I really am a fool.

174
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:09,440
You just realized you're a fool?

175
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,960
Weren't we having a nice chat?

176
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,960
Did you just rub salt in the wound?

177
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:16,080
You sprinkle salt on the chicken.

178
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,120
This...

179
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,560
Is this shrimp cooked?
